    "SUMMARY": "Chigozie Agbim  is a Nigerian professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper.\nAfter a protracted transfer dispute, he joined Enugu Rangers from Warri Wolves F.C. in April 2013 for a fee of eight million naira (approx €39,300).\nHe joined Gombe United in February 2014  and rejoined Rangers in April 2015."
